  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/smartphones/\" rel=\"tag\">智能手机</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/01/google-sync-windows-phone-support-extension/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/08/windowsphone.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n就在大家都以为从今往后 Windows Phone 将无法再启用 Google Sync 的<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/31/8-1-windows-phone-google-sync/\">时候</a>，Google 又做出了一个令人意外的决定。他们今天宣布将<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/01/31/google-exchange-activesync/\">再给</a> Windows Phone 用户 5 个月的时间，把停止服务的日期推迟到了 12 月 31 日。这样一来，微软应该就有足够的时间推送 GDR 2 更新了。那么在大家都转用 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/03/15/google-caldav-support-still-coming-to-windows-phon/\">CalDAV 和 CardDAV</a> 同步相关的 Google 服务以前，请允许我们先为 Google 点播一首小齐的「心太软」吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/08/01/google-sync-windows-phone-support-extension/\">Engadget</a>、<a href=\"http://www.theverge.com/2013/8/1/4577814/google-windows-phone-exchange-activesync-extension-december\" target=\"_blank\">The Verge</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://support.google.com/a/bin/answer.py?hl=en-uk&amp;hlrm=en&amp;answer=2716936\" target=\"_blank\">Google</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/01/google-sync-windows-phone-support-extension/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20683533/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/01/google-sync-windows-phone-support-extension/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
